

Options:
  -h --help	Display this help.

Commands:
  -z		Move forward or move faster forward (+0.1 speed).
  -s		Move backwards or move faster backwards (+0.1 speed).
  -q		Turn left or turn more on the left (-0.1 rotation).
  -d		Turn right or turn more on the right (+0.1 rotation).
  -space	Stop the vehicle and reset the wheels' rotation.
  -ESC		Quit the commands.

